'''湯馬士·祖舒亞·"湯姆"·艾利洛'''（{{lang-en|'''Thomas Joshua "Tom" Elliott'''}}，{{bd|1990年|11月9日|catIdx=Elliott ,Tom}}），簡稱'''湯姆·艾利洛'''（{{lang-en|'''Tom Elliott'''}}），是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]足球員，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，現效力[[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|英乙]]球會[[沙福特城足球會|沙福特城]]。

==球會==
;列斯聯
2007年2月3日，艾利洛在[[卡諾路球場|卡諾路球場]]對[[諾域治足球會|諾域治]]的賽事中後備入替而處子上陣<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6305265.stm |title=Norwich 2-1 Leeds |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2007-02-03 |accessdate=2010-08-14 |archive-date=2007-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070212170325/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6305265.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，成為[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯足球會]]首位在-{一}-隊處子上陣時仍然在學的球員<ref name="BIG TOM'S SCHOOLDAYS">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.leedsunited.com/news/20070208/big-toms-schooldays_2247585_978101 |title=BIG TOM'S SCHOOLDAYS |publisher=[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]] |date=2007-02-08 |accessdate=2010-08-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121123201444/http://www.leedsunited.com/news/20070208/big-toms-schooldays_2247585_978101 |archivedate=2012-11-23 }}</ref>。8月9日，他與球會簽訂職業合約，並在2008年夏天生效<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/6938514.stm |title=Leeds snap up midfielder Thompson |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2007-08-09 |accessdate=2010-08-14 |archive-date=2011-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110203003350/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/6938514.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2009年1月27日，艾利洛克服腿筋傷患以外借形式加盟[[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|英乙]]球會[[馬爾斯菲足球會|馬爾斯菲]]，為期一個月<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/macclesfield_town/7852804.stm |title=Elliott joins Silkmen on loan |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2009-01-27 |accessdate=2010-08-14 |archive-date=2009-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090130082120/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/macclesfield_town/7852804.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同日，他在以0-0逼和[[韋甘比足球會|韋甘比]]的賽事中後備入替而首次上陣<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7847945.stm |title=Macclesfield 0-0 Wycombe |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2009-01-27 |accessdate=2010-08-14 |archive-date=2009-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090130135553/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7847945.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2月14日，他在以0-1的比分不敵[[羅奇代爾足球會|羅奇代爾]]的賽事中首次正選上陣<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7876781.stm |title=Macclesfield 0-1 Rochdale |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2009-02-14 |accessdate=2010-08-14 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307133609/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7876781.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

9月16日，艾利洛被外借至[[貝利足球會|貝利]]，為期三個月<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11715_5563434,00.html |title=Elliott to join Shakers |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-09-16 |accessdate=2010-08-14 |archive-date=2010-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100111202425/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11715_5563434,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月19日，他在以1-0的比分擊敗[[維爾港足球會|維爾港]]的賽事中後備入替而處子上陣<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/8249052.stm |title=Port Vale   0 - 1   Bury |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2009-09-19 |accessdate=2010-08-14 |archive-date=2009-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090929010631/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/8249052.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月29日，他在以3-2的比分擊敗[[克魯足球會|克魯]]的賽事中攻入其職業生涯的首個入球<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/8271066.stm |title=Crewe   2 - 3   Bury |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2009-09-29 |accessdate=2010-08-14 |archive-date=2009-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091003050527/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/8271066.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月24日，他獲球會續借至5月<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.leedsunited.com/news/20091224/goalkeeper-loan-extension-for-united_2247585_1914705 |title=GOALKEEPER LOAN EXTENSION FOR UNITED |publisher=[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯足球會]] |date=2009-12-24 |accessdate=2010-08-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121122033403/http://www.leedsunited.com/news/20091224/goalkeeper-loan-extension-for-united_2247585_1914705 |archivedate=2012-11-22 }}</ref>。

2010年7月16日，艾利洛被球會外借至[[洛達咸足球會|洛達咸]]，為期半年<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/r/rotherham_utd/8826308.stm |title=Rotherham United sign Tom Elliott from Leeds United |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2010-07-15 |accessdate=2010-08-14 |archive-date=2010-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100731094252/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/r/rotherham_utd/8826308.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。8月7日，他在以2-1的比分擊敗[[林肯城足球會|林肯城]]的賽事中處子上陣<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/8842791.stm |title=Rotherham 2-1 Lincoln City |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2010-08-07 |accessdate=2010-08-14 |archive-date=2010-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100807210149/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/8842791.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;咸美頓
2011年1月31日艾利洛於被[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]棄用後以自由身加盟[[蘇超|蘇超]]球會[[咸美顿学院足球俱乐部|咸美頓]]，簽約至球季結束<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hamilton_academical/9382354.stm |title=Hamilton sign Leeds striker Tom Elliott |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-31 |accessdate=2011-02-01 |archive-date=2011-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110131213058/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hamilton_academical/9382354.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年5月14日，來季要降班的[[咸美顿学院足球俱乐部|咸美頓]]宣佈有8名球員不獲續約，艾利洛為其中之一<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13398942 |title=Hamilton wield axe for the drop |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-14 |accessdate=2013-11-07 |archive-date=2015-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150620234310/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13398942 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;史托港
2011年8月12日，艾利洛加盟[[英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽|英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽]]球會[[斯托克港足球俱乐部|史托港]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/14505252 |title=Stockport County add five new signings |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-08-12 |accessdate=2013-11-07 |archive-date=2014-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140903120015/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/14505252 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;劍橋聯
2012年5月23日，[[英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽|英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽]]球會[[剑桥联足球俱乐部|劍橋聯]]宣佈簽入拒絕續約[[斯托克港足球俱乐部|史托港]]的艾利洛，合約為期兩年7月1日生效<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/18180268 |title=Cambridge United sign Tom Elliott from Stockport County |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-05-23 |accessdate=2013-11-07 |archive-date=2014-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140827005012/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/18180268 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.stockport.vitalfootball.co.uk/article.asp?a=283045 |title=Tom Elliott Joins Cambridge |publisher=''www.stockport.vitalfootball.co.uk'' |date=2012-05-23 |accessdate=2013-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120726024556/http://www.stockport.vitalfootball.co.uk/article.asp?a=283045 |archive-date=2012-07-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

;沙福特城
2020年1月9日，艾利洛與[[沙福特城足球會|沙福特城]] 簽約2年半<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/51054656|title=Tom Elliott: Salford City sign Millwall striker on two-and-a-half-year deal|publisher=BBC|date=9 January 2020|accessdate=9 January 2020|archive-date=2020-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200203075020/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/51054656|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==國家隊==
2006年4月15日，艾利洛在對突尼西亞U16的賽事中首次代表[[英格蘭16歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U16]]上陣<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.thefa.com/England/All-Teams/Players/E/Tom-Elliott |title=Tom Elliott |publisher=[[英格蘭足球總會|英足總]] |date=2006-04-15 |accessdate=2010-08-14 |archive-date=2010-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100505211507/http://www.thefa.com/England/All-Teams/Players/E/Tom-Elliott |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2007年，他獲選代表[[英格蘭17歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U17]]出戰阿爾加威錦標賽（Algarve Tournament）<ref name="BIG TOM'S SCHOOLDAYS" />。

